<span id="freeTextContainer13869982565939088706">Funny in parts, interesting in some, but mostly just a load of tiring balderdash. <br/><br/>There are ways of retelling an old story thatâ€™s thoughtful and humorous, but this is not it. All the old stories become contrived and meaningless and have a weird climax that seems quite forced. The author seems to be quite a fun person, but I see this as a waste of his talent. This is a satire and a farce, but doesnâ€™t quite have the intelligence or the ability to evoke that laughter. It just gets boring. </span>

          </span>
